+| `evaluate` throws or does not return an array                      | Fail-loud log; the entire tick is skipped (no rows for any candidate). |
+| Decision carries a `writId` not in the candidate set               | Per-decision `console.warn` naming the offending id; ignore-and-continue. The rest of the tick proceeds. |
+| Two decisions target the same `writId`                             | Fail-loud log; the **entire tick** is skipped (no decision is applied to any candidate). |
+| Decision carries an unknown outcome                                | Fail-loud log; that one decision is ignored. The rest of the tick proceeds. |
+| Per-row `transition()` or `put()` throws                           | Per-row `console.warn`; the tick continues to the next candidate. |
 
