+  their own standing orders against `reckoner.tick` (with different
+  `with:` blocks) but cannot disable or override the kit-contributed
+  default — that is the additive-merge model from the kit-standing-
+  orders commission.
+- **No tick disable / pause mechanism.** Operators have no
+  config-side way to suspend the tick in this commission.
+- **No multi-scheduler dispatch in one tick.** One active scheduler
+  per Reckoner instance.
+- **No new framework events on tick.** The auto-wired Clockworks
